                            <comment id="15200322" author="szehon" created="Thu, 17 Mar 2016 20:36:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Chinna for working on the patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For this line:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    if (minReplication &amp;gt; dfsMaxRep)&lt;br/&gt;
	      minReplication = dfsMaxRep;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it possible to change it to minReplication = Math.max(minReplication, dfsMaxRep) (for clarity), and also put a comment explaining why?  Thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15201033" author="chinnalalam" created="Fri, 18 Mar 2016 05:29:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=szehon&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;szehon&quot;&gt;szehon&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;minReplication should not cross the dfsMaxReplication, so you mean to say it should be minReplication = Math.min(minReplication, dfsMaxReplication).&lt;br/&gt;
Patch was updated with Math.min(). Let me know if my understanding is wrong.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
